**Protocol:** WebSocket (or Server-Sent Events as fallback)

**Events:**

| Event | Direction | Trigger | Payload |
|-------|-----------|---------|---------|
| `player_joined` | Server → All Clients | Player joins room | `{ player_id, name, room_id }` |
| `player_left` | Server → All Clients | Player leaves room | `{ player_id, room_id }` |
| `round_started` | Server → All Clients | Host clicks START ROUND | `{ board: string[4][4], duration_seconds: 90, start_time: timestamp }` |
