| `word_validated` | Server → All Clients | Word validation complete | `{ player_id, word: string, is_valid: boolean, points: integer, error: string }` |
| `score_updated` | Server → All Clients | Player score changes | `{ player_id, current_score: integer, word_count: integer }` |
| `progress_updated` | Server → All Clients | Global word count updates | `{ unique_words_found: integer, total_possible: integer }` |
| `timer_tick` | Server → All Clients | Every 1 second (optional, for synced timer) | `{ seconds_remaining: integer }` |
| `round_ended` | Server → All Clients | Timer reaches 0 or host ends round | `{ rankings: Ranking[], answer_key: string[] }` |

