## 12. Security & Privacy Considerations

- **Session Management:** Use JWT or secure session cookies. Validate player token on every API call.
- **Input Validation:** Sanitize all text input (player names, room codes). Reject special characters in names.
- **Word List:** Use standardized, non-offensive dictionary (ENABLE list is appropriate).
- **Rate Limiting:** Implement server-side rate limiting to prevent abuse (submissions, room creation).
- **CORS:** Restrict API access to frontend domain only.
- **No PII Logging:** Avoid logging player names or detailed gameplay logs.
- **GDPR Compliance:** Allow players to delete account/game history (future phase).

